{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ever wondered what it's like to work in an electronics factory? \ud83e\uddd1\u200d\ud83c\udfed Now you can experience it! \u26a1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i><strong>Factory Life</strong></i>, you play as an ordinary worker assembling, testing, and packing equipment\u2014all under tight deadlines and a demanding boss. \ud83d\udc41\ufe0f Complete orders to earn money, but mistakes cost you both wages and factory progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start in a small, neglected workshop and build it into a thriving plant\u2014your precision and dedication determine success! \ud83c\udfed Ensure the factory's growth and secure a better future for your family. \ud83d\udc68\u200d\ud83d\udc69\u200d\ud83d\udc67</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key features of the game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd0b<strong>First-person experience of working on the production line</strong> - immerse yourself in a realistic simulation of work in a factory, from assembling electronic devices, through testing their operation, to final packing of orders. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_4_1.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfed<strong>Gradual development of the factory</strong> - each job well done allows you to unlock new positions, better equipment and larger orders. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_8.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_10.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcf1<strong>Various orders</strong> - a new game has come out and you need graphics cards? Or maybe a new smartphone was launched? All of these devices are manufactured in an electronics factory! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_7_1.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_13.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\uddd1\u200d\ud83c\udfed<strong>Realistic factory work simulation</strong> - feel like an employee of a small factory who, like a one-man army, deals with various aspects of work on the production line, must keep up with deadlines and support a family. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_3.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcc8<strong>Growing challenges</strong> \u2013 the more orders, the greater the pressure. Maintain high quality of work and avoid mistakes to earn as much money as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/extras/Factory_Gif_1.gif?t=1738761351\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you up to the challenge?\ud83d\udcaa</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738761351","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738761351","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462580/f3a75254665c69daa6f3bf690882f686edbf249f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738761351","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c